    "display_name": "Polish the Style",
    "long_instructions": "#Polish the Style\r\n\r\n## Do This:\r\n1. Prompt the AI to improve the button, links, and their hover/focus styles so they feel on-brand and easy to use.\r\n   - Don't forget to ensure the page still meets usability standards.\r\n\r\n::: details [Style Prompt Examples]\r\nTry these prompts to help you polish the style:\r\n- *Make the nav bar links feel interactive: add hover underline that animates, and a strong focus-visible outline.*\r\n- *Improve the [X] button so it looks distinct from [X] button, with a hover that doesn’t hurt contrast.*\r\n- *Give the links inside the cards a consistent style (default, hover, visited) with good readability.*\r\n:::",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Practice prompting AI to improve the buttons, links, and hover styles so they feel on-brand and easy to use.",
    "thumbnail_url": "https://images.code.org/9b2759fd37b4056b6d97792dd2693353-color-palette.png",
    "start_sources": {
      "folders": {
      },
      "files": {
        "1": {
          "id": "1",
          "name": "index.html",
          "language": "html",
          "contents": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Loop — Student Startup Landing Page</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n  <a class=\"skip-link\" href=\"#main\">Skip to content</a>\n\n  <header class=\"site-header\">\n    <div class=\"container header-inner\">\n      <a class=\"brand\" href=\"#home\" aria-label=\"Loop home\">\n        <span class=\"logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\">◯</span>\n        <span class=\"brand-name\">Loop</span>\n      </a>\n\n      <nav class=\"primary-nav\" aria-label=\"Primary\">\n        <ul class=\"nav\">\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#features\">Features</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#stories\">Stories</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#pricing\">Pricing</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n\n      <div class=\"header-cta\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-ghost\" href=\"#signin\">Sign in</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#signup\">Get Started</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main id=\"main\">\n    <!-- HERO -->\n    <section class=\"hero container\" id=\"home\">\n      <div class=\"hero-grid\">\n        <div class=\"hero-copy\">\n          <h1>Group projects, finally organized.</h1>\n          <p class=\"lede\">\n            Loop is a simple hub for teams at school — share tasks, track progress,\n            and keep everything in one place.\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"actions\">\n            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#signup\">Create a free workspace</a>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"#demo\">See a quick demo</a>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"micro-note\">No credit card required • Free for students</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-media\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <img\n            src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/loopdash/900/540\"\n            alt=\"\"\n            class=\"hero-img\"\n          />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- FEATURES -->\n    <section class=\"features container\" id=\"features\" aria-label=\"Features\">\n      <h2>Everything you need to ship on time</h2>\n      <div class=\"card-grid\">\n        <article class=\"card\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/tasks/640/360\" alt=\"Task list preview\" />\n          <h3>Tasks & Checklists</h3>\n          <p>Break big projects into steps. Assign owners and due dates.</p>\n          <a class=\"inline-link\" href=\"#learn-tasks\">Learn more</a>\n          <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\">Try it</button>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"card\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/chat/640/360\" alt=\"Chat bubbles illustration\" />\n          <h3>Focus Chat</h3>\n          <p>Keep project talk in one place — no more lost threads.</p>\n          <a class=\"inline-link\" href=\"#learn-chat\">Learn more</a>\n          <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\">Try it</button>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"card\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/files/640/360\" alt=\"Files and folders illustration\" />\n          <h3>Files, All Together</h3>\n          <p>Docs, slides, and links — organized by group and class.</p>\n          <a class=\"inline-link\" href=\"#learn-files\">Learn more</a>\n          <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\">Try it</button>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- STORIES -->\n    <section class=\"stories container\" id=\"stories\" aria-label=\"Student stories\">\n      <h2>Students are finishing faster</h2>\n      <blockquote class=\"quote\">\n        “We planned our robotics build in Loop and finished a week early.\n        Tasks + chat in one place = no chaos.”\n        <cite>— Maya T., Robotics Club</cite>\n      </blockquote>\n\n      <p>\n        Curious how teams use Loop? Check out our <a class=\"inline-link\" href=\"#blog\">blog</a>\n        for real student workflows and templates.\n      </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- PRICING / CTA -->\n    <section class=\"pricing container\" id=\"pricing\" aria-label=\"Pricing\">\n      <h2>Start free. Upgrade when you’re ready.</h2>\n      <div class=\"pricing-cta\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#signup\">Get Started</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-ghost\" href=\"#contact\">Contact us</a>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"micro-note\">Student plan includes 3 workspaces and unlimited collaborators.</p>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"site-footer\">\n    <div class=\"container footer-inner\">\n      <p>© 2025 Loop — a student-built project platform</p>\n      <nav aria-label=\"Footer\">\n        <ul class=\"nav footer-nav\">\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#privacy\">Privacy</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#terms\">Terms</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#support\">Support</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
          "active": false,
          "folderId": "0"
        },
        "2": {
          "id": "2",
          "name": "styles.css",
          "language": "css",
          "contents": "/* =========================\n   Brand tokens (intentionally plain)\n   ========================= */\n:root {\n  --brand-accent: #6c5ce7;          /* primary accent (purple) */\n  --brand-accent-hover: #6c5ce7;    /* same as accent (POLISH TARGET: differentiate) */\n  --brand-surface: #ffffff;\n  --brand-bg: #f4f5f8;\n  --brand-text: #1f2937;\n  --brand-muted: #6b7280;\n  --brand-border: #e5e7eb;\n\n  --radius: 8px;\n  --radius-sm: 4px;\n\n  --space-1: 4px;\n  --space-2: 8px;\n  --space-3: 12px;\n  --space-4: 16px;\n  --space-6: 24px;\n  --space-8: 32px;\n\n  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.06);\n  --shadow-md: 0 6px 14px rgba(0,0,0,.10);\n\n  --transition: 0s; /* no animation by default (POLISH TARGET: add motion & respect reduced motion) */\n}\n\n/* =========================\n   Base / reset-ish\n   ========================= */\n* { box-sizing: border-box; }\nhtml, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }\nbody {\n  font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial;\n  color: var(--brand-text);\n  background: var(--brand-bg);\n  line-height: 1.5;\n}\nimg { max-width: 100%; display: block; }\nh1, h2, h3 { line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0; }\np { margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0; }\n\n/* Skip link (kept functional) */\n.skip-link { position: absolute; left: -9999px; top: auto; }\n.skip-link:focus { left: 16px; top: 16px; background: #000; color:#fff; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }\n\n/* =========================\n   Layout\n   ========================= */\n.container { width: min(100%, 1080px); margin-inline: auto; padding: 0 var(--space-4); }\n\n.site-header {\n  background: var(--brand-surface);\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--brand-border);\n}\n.header-inner {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto auto;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: var(--space-4);\n  padding-block: var(--space-4);\n}\n.brand {\n  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2);\n  text-decoration: none; color: var(--brand-text); font-weight: 800;\n}\n.logo { color: var(--brand-accent); font-size: 1.25rem; }\n.brand-name { letter-spacing: .3px; }\n\n.nav { display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }\n\n/* =========================\n   NAV LINKS (UNDER-SPECIFIED ON PURPOSE)\n   ========================= */\n.primary-nav .nav-link {\n  text-decoration: none;               /* no underline (POLISH TARGET: improve discoverability) */\n  color: var(--brand-text);\n  padding: 6px 8px;\n  border-radius: 0;                    /* square corners (POLISH TARGET: unify radius) */\n  /* No transition (POLISH TARGET) */\n}\n.primary-nav .nav-link:hover {\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,.03);         /* very subtle hover (POLISH TARGET: clearer state / brand color) */\n}\n.primary-nav .nav-link:focus-visible {\n  outline: 1px dotted #999;            /* weak focus (POLISH TARGET: strong, consistent ring) */\n  outline-offset: 1px;\n}\n\n/* =========================\n   Hero\n   ========================= */\n.hero { padding-block: var(--space-8); }\n.hero-grid { display: grid; gap: var(--space-8); grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr; }\n.hero-copy .lede { color: var(--brand-muted); font-size: 1.05rem; }\n.actions { display: flex; gap: var(--space-3); margin-top: var(--space-4); }\n.micro-note { color: var(--brand-muted); font-size: .9rem; margin-top: var(--space-2); }\n.hero-img { border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }\n\n/* =========================\n   Features / cards\n   ========================= */\n.features { padding-block: var(--space-8); }\n.card-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-6); margin-top: var(--space-6); }\n.card {\n  background: var(--brand-surface);\n  border: 1px solid var(--brand-border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  padding: var(--space-4);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);\n}\n.card h3 { margin-top: var(--space-3); }\n.card p { color: var(--brand-muted); }\n.card .btn { margin-top: var(--space-2); }\n\n/* =========================\n   Stories / quote\n   ========================= */\n.stories { padding-block: var(--space-8); }\n.quote {\n  background: var(--brand-surface);\n  border: 1px solid var(--brand-border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  padding: var(--space-4);\n  font-style: italic;\n}\n\n/* =========================\n   Pricing / CTA\n   ========================= */\n.pricing { padding-block: var(--space-8); text-align: center; }\n.pricing-cta { display: inline-flex; gap: var(--space-3); margin-top: var(--space-3); }\n\n/* =========================\n   Footer\n   ========================= */\n.site-footer { background: var(--brand-surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--brand-border); margin-top: var(--space-8); }\n.footer-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-block: var(--space-4); }\n.footer-nav .nav-link { color: var(--brand-muted); }\n\n/* =========================\n   INLINE LINKS (NEEDS WORK)\n   ========================= */\n.inline-link {\n  color: var(--brand-accent);\n  text-underline-offset: 2px;\n  text-decoration: none;               /* no underline (POLISH TARGET: clearer default, visited/hover patterns) */\n}\n.inline-link:hover {\n  color: var(--brand-accent-hover);    /* same color (POLISH TARGET: differentiate or add underline) */\n}\n.inline-link:visited {\n  color: var(--brand-accent);          /* no visited differentiation (POLISH TARGET) */\n}\n.inline-link:focus-visible {\n  outline: 1px dotted #999;            /* weak/inconsistent vs. buttons/nav (POLISH TARGET) */\n  outline-offset: 1px;\n}\n\n/* =========================\n   BUTTONS (BASIC, INCONSISTENT)\n   ========================= */\n.btn {\n  --btn-bg: var(--brand-surface);\n  --btn-fg: var(--brand-text);\n  --btn-bd: var(--brand-border);\n\n  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n  padding: 10px 14px;\n  border-radius: 0;                    /* square corners (POLISH TARGET: radius consistency) */\n  border: 1px solid var(--btn-bd);\n  background: var(--btn-bg);\n  color: var(--btn-fg);\n  text-decoration: none;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  /* No transitions or shadows (POLISH TARGET: add motion and elevation) */\n}\n\n/* Primary (blunt states) */\n.btn-primary {\n  --btn-bg: var(--brand-accent);\n  --btn-fg: #fff;\n  --btn-bd: var(--brand-accent);\n}\n.btn-primary:hover {\n  background: var(--brand-accent-hover); /* but hover color == accent (POLISH TARGET: darker or different) */\n  border-color: var(--brand-accent-hover);\n}\n.btn-primary:active { /* no feedback besides brief color change (POLISH TARGET: transform/shadow) */ }\n.btn-primary:disabled,\n.btn-primary[aria-disabled=\"true\"] { opacity: .65; cursor: not-allowed; }\n\n/* Secondary (too similar to ghost, low emphasis) */\n.btn-secondary {\n  --btn-bg: var(--brand-surface);\n  --btn-fg: var(--brand-accent);\n  --btn-bd: var(--brand-accent);\n}\n.btn-secondary:hover {\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,.03);         /* neutral, not brand-aligned (POLISH TARGET) */\n}\n\n/* Ghost (indistinct) */\n.btn-ghost {\n  --btn-bg: transparent;\n  --btn-fg: var(--brand-text);\n  --btn-bd: var(--brand-border);\n}\n.btn-ghost:hover {\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,.03);         /* same as others (POLISH TARGET: differentiate) */\n}\n\n/* Focus states (inconsistent and weak) */\n.btn:focus-visible {\n  outline: 1px dotted #999;            /* POLISH TARGET: unify with links/nav, increase visibility */\n  outline-offset: 1px;\n}\n\n/* Disabled clarity kept */\n.btn[disabled],\n.btn[aria-disabled=\"true\"] { cursor: not-allowed; opacity: .6; }\n",
          "folderId": "0",
          "active": true
        }
      },
      "openFiles": [
        "1",
        "2"
      ]
    },
